Get pet up to 10 times!
1) Make sure you have your props set up how you want them! Make a separate prop for each position that you want the petting to be. Make sure they're set to hidden after!2) Make sure all "Toggle Prop" nodes have a different petting prop in them. I Made sure to color each group together to make it easier.3) Set your redeem name (or however you have your pets toggled, bits commands, etc)4) Set a hotkey to toggle all of them as hidden! (Just in case something goes wrong)Note: If one gets toggled again, it simply extends the time that one is active and will still go off after the timer stops.
